\fBCC\fR
.RS 4
The C compiler\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBCCCOM\fR
.RS 4
The command line used to compile a C source file to a (static) object file\&. Any options specified in the
\fB$CFLAGS\fR,
\fB$CCFLAGS\fR
and
\fB$CPPFLAGS\fR
construction variables are included on this command line\&. See also
\fB$SHCCCOM\fR
for compiling to shared objects\&.
